= Getting ready for OIT: equipment and how to use
== Equipment list

1. 1 ml disposable syringes without the needles. They should have 0.1 ml increments marked on the side of the syringe.
- Example: BD eclipse 1mL oral syringes or Terumo 1mL oral tuberculin syringes (available on amazon.ca or local pharmacies).

2. Weight scale, with precision of 0.01 grams. Purchase a scale with two decimal places, with calibration weight. Scales are usually in the \$20-30 price range and can be easily found online (e.g. Amazon).
