= Giving doses: checklist, how to give, when to increase

== Giving doses
- Checklist before daily dose
  - Make sure nutritional label protein content matches
  - Avoid strenuous exertion (makes them sweat)
  - sick with fever
  - no empty stomach
  - monitorable for 2 hours
- keep the food consistent don't switch forms
- Avoid naps or bedtime within 2 hours of dose

== What to expect from the first few doses
- ensure good lip care to avoid quick absorption, consider petroleum jelly before and after each dose.
- Taking Reactine 1 hour before daily dose during build-up can minimize mild side effects.

== When to increase dose
- min time 2 weeks
- depending on phys / talk / reactions etc may spend longer
- but if on 2 weeks and no sx prob good to go up

